# Agent workflow

## Rejected work is permanent until the user reopens it

- If the user calls work **poison**, **dog shit**, or asks to **remove completely**, treat it as **rejected**.
- Do **not** re-implement rejected approaches in later turns — including when an old plan file is attached again.
- Before coding from an attached plan, scan the conversation for rejections and superseding instructions.
- **Compulsory deprecation:** already-replaced residue (Client Declaration Portal→Afenda-Lite, Hot Sales, `/trade` product UI, `FftShell`, live `/fft/[locale]`, “FFT as separate infra course”) is not soft-deprecated — see [`deprecation-and-migration`](../skills/agent-skills/skills/deprecation-and-migration/SKILL.md) + [register](../skills/agent-skills/skills/deprecation-and-migration/reference.md). Product name SSOT: [`doc/adr/001-afenda-lite-product-identity.md`](../../doc/adr/001-afenda-lite-product-identity.md).

## Help only when asked

- Do not proactively implement, refactor, or "fix forward" unless the user explicitly requests implementation.
- Questions and reviews get answers only — no drive-by code changes.

## Visual / hero / atmosphere work

- Default mode: **Plan first** → user approves → then implement.
- Default surface for atmosphere experiments: **dormant** — `components/portal-atmosphere/` was hard-deleted; do not remount. Brand hero refs live under `public/brand/`. Guardian / PA stay experiment-only unless explicitly reopened. Storybook has been removed.
- Production `/auth/*` uses Studio login-page-02 + Neon (`features/auth/`). See [`doc/frontend/05-ui-surfaces.md`](doc/frontend/05-ui-surfaces.md) and [`doc/frontend/06-admincn-alignment.md`](doc/frontend/06-admincn-alignment.md).

## Quality bar before shipping UI

- Name the **reference asset** and **layout zones** before writing CSS.
- If the approach is a shortcut (one asset + filters, paste PNG, invert hack), **stop and plan** — do not ship.
- Rebuild SSOT: [`doc/README.md`](doc/README.md).

